{"type":"file-history-snapshot","messageId":"345a7e3e-28db-4489-b8ff-cedc59a74887","snapshot":{"messageId":"345a7e3e-28db-4489-b8ff-cedc59a74887","trackedFileBackups":{},"timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:42:18.284Z"},"isSnapshotUpdate":false}
{"parentUuid":"4530d054-1dc1-4eb6-a121-0590d49a2132","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"d82b98e8-1e3d-44d0-bb19-a18969fdd0d4","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"背面画像のサイズって？それでグリッドのサイズが決まるの？なぜ画像扱いになるの？"},"uuid":"345a7e3e-28db-4489-b8ff-cedc59a74887","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:42:15.037Z","permissionMode":"default","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"91c9eee4-7fa0-4d00-9434-ae3235d0772e","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"master"}
{"parentUuid":"345a7e3e-28db-4489-b8ff-cedc59a74887","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01NRdp2sp9yEwh4vrRJNUJmj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":751,"cache_read_input_tokens":17493,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":751},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CZiS7R77hUEXkQFtPhx9G","type":"assistant","uuid":"021cd026-8d24-4674-a0c1-aedb75252758","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:42:21.341Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"91c9eee4-7fa0-4d00-9434-ae3235d0772e","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"master"}
{"parentUuid":"021cd026-8d24-4674-a0c1-aedb75252758","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01NRdp2sp9yEwh4vrRJNUJmj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**背景サイズは 48px × 48px** → これがグリッド1マスのサイズになります。\n\n---\n\n**なぜ「画像」扱いなのか**\n\nCSS の `linear-gradient()` は、色を塗る関数ではなく **`<image>` 型を返す関数**として仕様上定義されています。\n\n```css\n/* これは background-color */\nbackground-color: red;\n\n/* これは background-image（グラデーションも「画像」）*/\nbackground-image: linear-gradient(red, blue);\n```\n\nなので `background-size` が適用でき、繰り返し（`background-repeat: repeat`、デフォルト）と組み合わせることでタイル状に並びます。\n\n---\n\n**グリッドが描かれる仕組み**\n\n```\n48px × 48px の「透明な正方形の左上端に1px線が引かれた画像」が繰り返される\n\n┌─────────────────────────────┐\n│ ←1px線→                     │\n│                              │  ← この画像が繰り返される\n│   (transparent)              │\n│                              │\n└─────────────────────────────┘\n  ↑ 1px線（90deg）\n```\n\n- 横線: `linear-gradient(var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px)` → 上端1pxだけ色付き、残り47px透明\n- 縦線: `linear-gradient(90deg, ...)` → 左端1pxだけ色付き、残り47px透明\n\nこの2枚が重なってタイル状に繰り返されることで、48px間隔のグリッドに見えます。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":751,"cache_read_input_tokens":17493,"output_tokens":498,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":751,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZiS7R77hUEXkQFtPhx9G","type":"assistant","uuid":"0c945759-0648-4739-9ff0-6eaeca49529c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:42:29.652Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"91c9eee4-7fa0-4d00-9434-ae3235d0772e","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"master"}
